# 🐍 Python Exercises - 40 Basic Programs

![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.x-blue.svg)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-green.svg)
![Exercises](https://img.shields.io/badge/Exercises-40-brightgreen.svg)

## 📚 Overview

This repository contains **40 Python exercises** covering fundamental programming concepts. Perfect for beginners learning Python or anyone looking to refresh their basics. Each exercise focuses on different aspects of Python programming including loops, conditionals, functions, data structures, and pattern printing.

## 📁 Exercise List

### 🔄 Loops & Basic Operations (1-10)
| # | Exercise | File |
|---|----------|------|
| 1 | Print numbers 1-20 using while loop | `exercise1.py` |
| 2 | Print numbers 1-20 using for loop | `exercise2.py` |
| 3 | Print all even numbers (1-50) | `exercise3.py` |
| 4 | Print all odd numbers (1-50) | `exercise4.py` |
| 5 | Print numbers 30-1 in reverse | `exercise5.py` |
| 6 | Print your name 10 times | `exercise6.py` |
| 7 | Print numbers divisible by 3 (1-100) | `exercise7.py` |
| 8 | Print numbers divisible by 5 and 7 (1-100) | `exercise8.py` |
| 9 | Find sum of numbers 1-50 | `exercise9.py` |
| 10 | Find sum of even numbers (1-100) | `exercise10.py` |

