## 🚀 Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.x installed on your system
- Any text editor or IDE (VS Code, PyCharm, etc.)

### Installation
```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/mhasanpy/exercise40python.git

# Navigate to the directory
cd exercise40python

# Run any exercise
python exercise1.py
